Upstream-Name: Chromium's Compact Language Detector
Upstream-Contact: Matt Sanford <matt@mzsanford.com>
Source: https://github.com/mzsanford/cld
Comments:
 This package contains the CLD (Compact Language Detection) library,
 extracted from the source code for Google's Chromium library at
 <URL:http://src.chromium.org/svn/trunk/src/third_party/cld>, specifically revision 105735.
 .
 The original extraction was done by Mike McCandless and was altered to improve
 the build and packaging as well as add new bindings for various languages.
 .
 The LICENSE is the same as Chromium's LICENSE and is included in the LICENSE file for reference.

